name: Resignation 01
description:
Succumbing to ones situation in life. Stuck in a situation, perhaps with another lifeform…if you’re lucky. That moment where you realise your struggle actually had no effort. Any movement was all in your head. You were always one block in the paving. You just didn’t realise. So you are here now.You finally see it. 

I WANT TO ROLL
BUT YOU HOLD ME HERE 
YOUR CEMENT 
BECOMING MOSS
WE ALL FALL IN LINE.
